<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/uk-council-for-internet-safety> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The UK Council for Internet Safety (UKCIS) is a collaborative forum through which government, the tech community and the third sector work together to ensure the UK is the safest place in the world to be online. UKCIS is part of the Department for Education , the Home Office , and the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology ."@en .
